jobs_results.title: Senior Android Developer (Kotlin) to Paf
jobs_results.description: Paf focuses on creating exciting, everyday entertainment that lasts. They lead the way in the industry where responsible gaming is the backbone of the company and they are united by the ambition to make a difference in the gaming industry. They strive for a long-term sustainable business and care about their employees, customers, and society; All profit goes to charity. - 'From day one our vision and strategies have been aligned with generating __long-term sustainable profit __to support the society. That’s the sole reason we exist.'_ OFFER As a developer at Paf, you will work in a close-knit team with colleagues who share a passion for delivering top-quality products, enabling great gaming experiences for a global and diverse audience. Paf is different from other game companies on the market. They strive for a long-term sustainable business and care about their employees, customers, and society; All profit goes to charity. - What's in it for you as an employee?_ - Flexible working hours to make your everyday life easier. - Generous terms regarding pensions, wellness, and free healthcare. - They avoid overtime; you staying with them for 10 years is more important than short-term business goals. - Work Location: You decide_ - Office located in central Stockholm and Norrköping - Home office: You will be given a desk, screens, and docking station for your home office as well as paid Wi-fi. - A hybrid arrangement, where you work from the office a few days each week. - You can also choose to work abroad for 3 months a year. THE TEAM & PRODUCT The role takes place in their frontend team that focuses on their apps (for both iOS and Android), as well as the entire stack beneath them. These casino apps operate across various markets and brands and the team is responsible for the entire stack, from app development to the underlying infrastructure in AWS. The team you'll be joining is highly experienced, fostering an open-minded atmosphere where everyone's contribution is valued. You will enter the product in an early stage that will continue to be developed for a long time ahead - granting you a lot of freedom to set the frames with the team, working with both improvement and innovation. Check their tech-radar out to see which technologies are coming, which they use, and which they are phasing out. YOUR ROLE We are in search of a senior developer who is both curious and passionate about modern Android development in Kotlin. You should feel confident taking initiative on your own, but also equally comfortable collaborating with others. Being driven and proactive, you won't hesitate to ask for assistance when needed. Extra interesting if you also have experience with: - iOS development - Typescript - AWS or other cloud platforms They don’t look too much at formal education and diplomas, a lot can be compensated with: - Good communication skills - Track record as a team player - Independence - Accountability - Experience and knowledge MORE ABOUT PAF: - Paf is a Nordic gaming company founded on Åland in 1966 to generate profit for the benefit of society. They were one of the very first gaming companies to go online in 1999. Many of their games are exclusive to Paf and developed by their in-house Games Studio. They are an award-winning industry leader in responsible gaming. Their physical gaming operations include over 30 cruise ships crisscrossing the Baltic and North Seas._ - Paf has roughly 330 employees representing 29 nationalities, with offices located in Åland, Helsinki, Stockholm, Riga, Tallinn, Oslo, Norrköping, Gzira, and Madrid. Paf (Ålands Penningautomatförening) is licensed and controlled by the Government of Åland._ - In 2022, the Paf Group had a total turnover of 165,7 million euros and a profit of 44,4 million euros. _ ABOUT PINETREE At Pinetree, we have a vision and mission to differentiate ourselves from the crowd and are Sweden's contenders in talent search and matching. By working as an agency, the value to you as an employee is that we have a very wide network of partner companies that we continuously ensure their high-quality standards.
